snippet.title: IF ~Imaginary friends~
snippet.description:
Game Release
I am pleased to announce the release of my self-made indie game “IF - Imaginary Friends”.
It is an adventure game with a picture book-like worldview and picturesque textures.
The download page can be found at the following link
https://10mixel.itch.io/
